{"tid":2179424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊入嚟搞鳩荷蘭叻條pk","createTime":"2020-08-29T05:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T15:47:42.000Z","uid":335967,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3775d8eb14719e4a2c1a3a5fb61bca078282e9c9","tid":2179424,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:56:38.000Z","msg":"【一鍵投訴違法僭建暴徒&ldquo;荷蘭叻&rdquo;！】<br />\n<br />\n唔想荷蘭叻繼續犯法做暴亂分子，一齊做：<br />\n（1）&ldquo;分享&rdquo; 呢個post出去、去連登開文幫推<br />\n（2）使用以下連結作一鍵投訴 （記得最底位置改名，部分手機可能不支援，留言有template可作修改參考）<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3935V0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3935V0g&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=d3373bf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3935V0g</a><br />\n<br />\n壹週刊踢爆荷蘭叻豪宅有多處違法超過10年的僭建物！藐視屋宇署清拆令！ <a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/Ee7Wk0xMh9q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2FEe7Wk0xMh9q&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=1fdab661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/Ee7Wk0xMh9q</a><br />\n<br />\n你犯法就當然唔關壹週刊嘅事，而係我哋每一個香港人嘅事，你違法僭建，無視屋宇署2008年嘅清拆令，一邊口講支持政府，另一邊就明目張膽做僭建暴亂分子，大型僭建物一旦倒塌，隨時累己累人！<br />\n<br />\n轉載請註明出處：專業清算師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=0d3ed39c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevengehi&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=670f5794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/revengehi</a>"},{"pid":"a15967a1bd919fc3aa0eb8d12624f8ace7e43953","tid":2179424,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e196498131b52e93eaa1117467e08eab4868a1a8","tid":2179424,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ffc643b6d5eacac77fc9f91ad391aba39abbb9","tid":2179424,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"wow <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65f737ad1dd61e67189f98ed075acee863d7fd3","tid":2179424,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1354ec10a21d97d1de993e62c64fbbee1c29a37","tid":2179424,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f865e327c314015a8177042525b11666d123acdd","tid":2179424,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"推左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e76bfa82ef36f2cf9497f577daba48729e524e","tid":2179424,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c40af003380336f4b1720b9c64e7c6d1988bd5a","tid":2179424,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0